headline: Cintas (NASDAQ:CTAS) Exceeds Q4 CY2025 Expectations
summary: Uniform and facility services provider Cintas (NASDAQ:CTAS) reported Q4 CY2025 results beating Wall Street’s revenue expectations, with sales up 9.3% year on year to $2.8 billion. The company expects the full year’s revenue to be around $11.19 billion, close to analysts’ estimates. Its GAAP profit of $1.21 per share was 1.3% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
